#+title: update-bf-uefi

* Credits

Andreis

* Image location and unzip

    The image can be found at /home/na2e/public/bootimage_update_3.7.zip

    Copy it to smd root:

        cp /home/na2e/public/bootimage_update_3.7.zip /root

    unzip it with following command:

        unzip -o /root/ bootimage_update_3.7.zip -d /

** Check if files are ok

    The files should have unzipped into the following directories and with
    respective lengths

    |  Length |       Date |  Time | Name                                            |
    | 2389080 | 10-05-2021 | 06:39 | diskless/blueos/2.0/reldir/BootImage/LD.bfb     |
    | 2389080 | 10-05-2021 | 06:39 | diskless/blueos/2.0/reldir/BootImage/SOD.bfb    |
    |   19972 | 09-13-2021 | 08:40 | diskless/blueos/2.0/reldir/Scripts/BFInstall.sh |
    |   12466 | 10-12-2021 | 07:06 | root/update_bootimage                           |
